abstract: United States wins women's 800-meter relay at Penn Relays in Philadelphia; other races noted.
lead_paragraph: Porscha Lucas led the United States team to victory in the women’s 800-meter relay at the Penn Relays, and the Americans won four of six events in the U.S.A. vs. The World races.
